name: Cave Painting (14/11/2021 PHOENIX)
description: An artwork in the Cave Painting Series by the artist M Plummer-Fernández. Created and minted 14/11/2021, acknowledging the fall and communal restoration and re-imagining of Hic Et Nunc, making this mint possible. The Cave Paintings are produced by a custom neural network system that projects visions onto imaginary caves in response to prompts chosen by the artist.
